    "With the advent of Nazism in Germany, Wind, a Jew, played a key role in moving the Warburg library to London along with himself and, with <a href=\"/wittkowerr\">Rudolf Wittkower</a>, founded the <em>Journal of the Warburg and Courtauld Institute</em> in 1937.": [],
